27:17.488 --> 27:20.789
Daniel?

27:20.791 --> 27:24.259
Daniel?

27:24.261 --> 27:26.361
What?

27:26.363 --> 27:28.529
Can we speak with you?

27:28.531 --> 27:30.965
Uh, okay.

27:40.709 --> 27:43.044
How ya doin', buddy?

27:43.046 --> 27:45.213
Very well.
How are you?

27:45.215 --> 27:49.050
Well, we're worried
about ya, honey.

27:49.052 --> 27:50.485
Why?

27:50.487 --> 27:55.356
- Well--
- Because we love you.

27:55.358 --> 27:57.926
Love is patient and kind.

27:57.928 --> 28:04.232
Love is not jealous,
or boastful, or proud.

28:08.771 --> 28:10.572
That's a lot of money.

28:10.574 --> 28:12.440
Is it?

28:12.442 --> 28:14.909
For cash, looks like it.

28:14.911 --> 28:17.045
You think it was ill-gotten?

28:17.047 --> 28:19.114
No.

28:19.116 --> 28:21.250
I don't think that.

28:21.252 --> 28:23.285
Mother?

28:23.287 --> 28:25.654
I don't know, Daniel.

28:25.656 --> 28:28.624
I don't, either.

28:28.626 --> 28:30.860
I have to get ready.

28:30.862 --> 28:33.262
Where ya headed?

28:33.264 --> 28:34.697
You don't know?

28:34.699 --> 28:36.098
We know.

28:36.100 --> 28:39.367
Well, if you know,
then why did you ask?

28:39.369 --> 28:41.569
Because we don't know how
to talk to you, honey.

28:41.571 --> 28:44.038
Just talk-- say it.

28:44.040 --> 28:45.005
What?

28:45.007 --> 28:49.743
