- Being saved?

28:56.084 --> 28:58.285
Maybe you should sleep on it.

28:58.287 --> 28:59.753
Have you been gettin'
much sleep?

28:59.755 --> 29:01.355
Can you guarantee I'll be here?

29:01.357 --> 29:02.189
What do you mean?

29:02.191 --> 29:03.957
It could happen at any time.

29:03.959 --> 29:05.159
What could?

29:05.161 --> 29:10.731
Anything-- anything could
happen at any time.

29:10.733 --> 29:14.335
Oh... and now, I
don't have time.

29:14.337 --> 29:16.070
Time? Daniel?

29:16.072 --> 29:17.739
- Daniel, please?
- Please what?

29:17.741 --> 29:19.574
Please be the way
you want me to be?

29:19.576 --> 29:21.442
No. I just want you to be happy.

29:21.444 --> 29:23.511
I will be happy.

29:23.513 --> 29:25.280
When I'm cleansed,
I will be happy.

29:25.282 --> 29:26.281
Daniel, please?

29:26.283 --> 29:28.583
I don't know how
you want me to be!

29:28.585 --> 29:32.887
- But, Daniel--
- I'm not even sure if I'm alive!

29:32.889 --> 29:37.592
- Oh... honey--
- Just stop!

29:37.594 --> 29:39.294
Stop living your life
for me, Amantha.

29:39.296 --> 29:44.632
I never asked you to, ever!

29:44.634 --> 29:52.340
Now, please, I'd like to walk
through that door like a person.

