34:07.704 --> 34:10.606
Daniel: I feel I
have reason, now.

34:10.608 --> 34:13.542
Tawney: Yes, you do.

34:13.543 --> 34:19.083
Just to-to be here,
to be right here--

34:20.518 --> 34:22.251
God has a plan for you, Daniel.

34:22.253 --> 34:24.018
I'm alive, Tawney.

34:24.021 --> 34:27.021
Hmm... I would say so.

34:27.023 --> 34:30.525
I thought I was dead
when I was in there.

34:30.527 --> 34:36.231
You know, and out here, I-I
still didn't believe it,

34:36.233 --> 34:38.367
that I was alive.

34:38.369 --> 34:41.136
It-it was like a-- I
thought it was like

34:41.138 --> 34:43.272
a dead man's dream, you know?

34:43.274 --> 34:46.408
You'll never die now, Daniel.

34:46.409 --> 34:48.443
Will you ever die, Tawney?

34:48.445 --> 34:51.213
No.

34:51.215 --> 34:53.081
I'm so glad.

34:53.083 --> 34:57.486
[ Laughter ]

34:57.488 --> 34:59.689
[ Crying ]

34:59.691 --> 35:02.325
Hey, don't be ashamed.

35:02.327 --> 35:05.194
God is releasing your pain.

35:05.196 --> 35:06.963
Where does it go?

35:06.965 --> 35:11.000
He takes it.

35:11.002 --> 35:14.437
You make me so happy, Tawney.

35:14.439 --> 35:21.912
It's Jesus who makes
you happy, not me.

35:21.914 --> 35:24.081
What?

35:24.083 --> 35:26.851
You know, the goat man told me
it's the beauty, not the ugly,

35:26.853 --> 35:29.487
that hurts the most.

35:29.489 --> 35:30.789
The goat man?

35:30.791 --> 35:31.856
I was with him today.

35:31.858 --> 35:38.630
We-we walked, and we gathered
all the goats together.

35:38.632 --> 35:41.199
And there was this girl,
and she had a head of

35:41.201 --> 35:45.937
another girl in her hands, and--
but, she had a goat's body.

35:45.939 --> 35:52.277
And that was after I-I'd
gone to her window.

35:52.279 --> 35:53.945
Whose window?

35:53.947 --> 35:55.481
And we wrestled.

35:55.483 --> 35:58.117
I knew I was wrestling
with myself.

35:58.119 --> 36:00.085
And he could've won.

36:00.087 --> 36:07.460
He had me, but he helped me
up, and we walked together.

36:07.462 --> 36:13.866
And the tall man at the store led
me back-- back to my father.

36:13.868 --> 36:16.035
To your father?

36:16.037 --> 36:18.437
To Ted's, back to Ted's, and
to the Father, the Son,

36:18.439 --> 36:26.245
and the Holy Ghost, and-and
finally, back here to you.

36:26.247 --> 36:28.280
May I kiss you, Tawney?

36:29.316 --> 36:33.519
[ Music ]

36:34.788 --> 36:38.238
I'm sorry. I shouldn't
have said that. That--

36:40.532 --> 36:42.193
It's okay.

36:42.195 --> 36:46.964
- You're just--
- Filled with the spirit.

36:46.966 --> 36:49.534
Yes?

36:49.536 --> 36:51.669
Yes.

36:51.671 --> 36:54.981
[ Music ]

36:57.210 --> 36:59.577
How about I call
your mama, Daniel?

36:59.579 --> 37:03.080
No.

37:03.082 --> 37:07.852
Thank you for
everything, Tawney.

37:07.854 --> 37:10.455
Let me give you a ride home.

37:10.457 --> 37:12.590
You're all wet.

37:12.592 --> 37:17.462
One day, maybe I'll let
you give me a ride home.

37:21.401 --> 37:23.335
I like it out here.

37:28.108 --> 37:32.379
Do you feel all the life?

37:32.381 --> 37:34.982
I do.

37:41.689 --> 37:43.823
Maybe there is a God.

37:56.103 --> 37:57.937
Good-bye, Tawney.

38:00.774 --> 38:03.533
[ Music ]

38:10.651 --> 38:13.919
[ Sighs ]

38:28.003 --> 38:29.737
Damn it, dad.

38:29.739 --> 38:34.408
[ Sighs ]

38:34.410 --> 38:37.861
Stupid idea.

38:51.559 --> 38:56.396
Hey, Ted!

38:56.398 --> 38:58.131
Don't kill him.

38:58.133 --> 39:04.070
Let him dance.

39:04.072 --> 39:05.605
Sure, buddy.

39:07.742 --> 39:10.444
Ugh...

39:20.154 --> 39:22.822
So, you did the deed, huh?

39:22.824 --> 39:25.291
I did.

39:25.293 --> 39:27.527
How was it?

39:27.529 --> 39:29.161
Fantastical.

39:29.163 --> 39:30.830
[ Laughter ]

39:30.832 --> 39:32.665
Fantastical, huh?

39:37.804 --> 39:38.938
You want some coffee?

39:38.940 --> 39:41.707
You can watch your
friend from inside.

39:41.709 --> 39:43.809
I like coffee.

39:54.120 --> 39:57.089
So, all your sins are
forgiven now, huh?

39:57.091 --> 40:00.158
That must be a load off.

40:00.160 --> 40:02.360
I'm not sure.

40:02.362 --> 40:05.396
Not sure about what?

40:05.398 --> 40:11.935
Seemed so, at first, that I
had truly been cleansed.

40:11.937 --> 40:20.242
- But then, I-- it's confusing-- I--
- Nothing confusing.

40:20.244 --> 40:22.945
Your sins are either
forgiven, or they're not.

40:22.947 --> 40:26.782
Doesn't seem so black
and white, Ted.

40:26.784 --> 40:28.984
[ Laughter ]

40:28.986 --> 40:31.787
Cut the shit, buddy.

40:31.789 --> 40:34.323
It's me you're talkin' to.

40:34.325 --> 40:35.959
That's right.

40:35.961 --> 40:39.830
I don't buy your lost
soul lie for a minute.

40:39.832 --> 40:42.533
You didn't wanna get
right with God.

40:42.535 --> 40:47.772
You wanted to get right with my
wife, right in bed with her.

40:47.774 --> 40:49.608
No-- no-- that's not true.

40:49.610 --> 40:51.877
Listen.
You want a piece of ass?

40:51.879 --> 40:55.114
Then you go pick up some skank
at the bar, but you stay

40:55.116 --> 40:57.250
the hell away from my Tawney.

40:57.252 --> 40:59.685
You hear me?

40:59.687 --> 41:03.456
She's out of bounds, off limits.

41:03.458 --> 41:08.527
Is that clear enough?

41:08.529 --> 41:10.363
Yes.

41:10.365 --> 41:12.665
I-I shouldn't be around her.

41:12.667 --> 41:16.602
Hell, I'm not sure you
should be around anybody.

41:16.604 --> 41:19.572
Stay the hell away from
me while you're at it.

41:21.809 --> 41:25.566
[ Music ]

41:32.553 --> 41:35.155
You know, one thing's
just been buggin'

41:35.157 --> 41:38.491
the shit out of me.

41:38.493 --> 41:40.894
What's that?

41:40.896 --> 41:43.296
When you was telling me that
sickening shower story,

41:43.298 --> 41:44.765
which I still don't understand
why you told me somethin'

41:44.767 --> 41:46.467
- like that--
- You asked.

41:46.469 --> 41:51.305
But, when you said how
it doesn't do any good

41:51.307 --> 41:54.408
to fight back, you know,
'cause there was too many

41:54.410 --> 41:56.310
of 'em or somethin'--
you remember that?

41:56.312 --> 41:58.579
You remember saying that?

41:58.581 --> 42:01.715
I do remember that.

42:01.717 --> 42:07.821
Now, what I wanna know is,
is did you fight back?

42:07.823 --> 42:12.960
Or, did you just
relax and enjoy it?

42:17.498 --> 42:18.999
It's not that simple.

42:19.001 --> 42:22.302
It's exactly that simple.

42:22.304 --> 42:24.671
There are things you don't know.

42:24.673 --> 42:29.042
[ Laughter ]

42:29.044 --> 42:32.945
Yeah-- well, long as
there's things you know.

42:32.947 --> 42:39.218
